{"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents13OUDSRadioItemV","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSRadioItem"},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some radios components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": like the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The radio indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Rescue from this world!\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"See ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/90c467-radio-button","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioitem_enabled_selected_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Business Tools","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioitem_enabled_selected_OrangeBusinessTools"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Inverse","anchor":"Orange-Inverse","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioitem_enabled_selected_OrangeInverse"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioitem_enabled_selected_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioitem_enabled_selected_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Version","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"Since","style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/init(isOn:label:additionalLabel:helper:icon:flipIcon:isOutlined:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUD